\pard\plain \fi720\sl288\slmult1\ltrch\loch \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1  Moto would lead them into a dead end, and everyone hated him. Then Moto would lead them into a windowed hall flush with fresh night air, and everyone loved him. }
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Seb tripped up and went sprawling down a stair, and Mandri hated her. Mandri slipped on a spot of Seb\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s spit, and, well, Mandri still hated her\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 Seb was the sole exception to this alternating}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Moto was dragging them into the pits of exasperation.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Let me see your sword.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93What?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Let me see it!\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Mandri fumbled at his sword\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s hilt. As he pulled it out he dropped it. It clanged on the stone floor, and in this cavernous hall the noise was magnified to a peal of thunder.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Moto clenched his jaw tight and his eyes accused Mandri of dropping the sword on purpose. Then he lowered his torch to the blade and studied the sheen of light playing upon it. He was looking for signs of use.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1  At pace, they reached the end of the hall unmolested, and uplifted there, on a narrow set of stairs, was a red sandstone throne.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 The throne\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s seat and arms were featureless, fashioned from natural river-smoothed stone, while its back was a billowing slab carved to look like flame licked into a curl by an unseen wind. Etched into the wall behind was a ring of faces, faces inside of faces, much like the temple\u8217\'92s exterior\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 howling animals, untamed men, as well as snarling demons.}}